reviewText: Revealing selection of interviews shows the education of Katy as she conversates with the elite of the international scene. Highlights her many "looks" as well.

BORING!  Just one talk after another.  And the interviews were not even all that great.  This is an Unauthorized dvd.  So, nothing really felt up and personal.  I wasted $30, and spent less than $5 on Kay Perry's Part of Me video.  I would've paid that amount for Part of her anytime!
My 19 and 13 year old girls are huge fans of KP, but did not like this dvd at all, it was too boring for them, and it was too expensive for me.

Ordered this for my niece who is undoubtedly in love with Katy, and she loved it! I watched it with her, and I personally wish we had seen more of Katy Perry herself talking about her life, but overall great Dvd!
Awesome, Just when I thought I knew everything about KP, this was better than " Behind the Music" Katy You Rock!!!!!!!
my daughter is a very big Katy Perry fan.  she will be so excited when she opens this at Christmas time.
